description: Capacity and Support programme to the Council of Representatives “CoR”

subproject.corporate outcome: Electoral laws, processes and institutions strengthen inclusive participation and professional electoral administration
subproject.description:
1: CoR administration and targeted parliamentary committees strengthened to improve their role in amending and reviewing laws and oversight functions in relation to conflict prevention and recovery
2: Engagement of the CoR with citizens enhanced to improve CoR contribution to social cohesion and dialogue and improved service delivery 
3: Capacity of Women Parliamentarians enhanced to contribute to State building and Peace building (UNSC 1325)
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: Support the Council of Rep.

title: Capacity & Support program to Council of Representatives
